{
    "data": [
        {
            "title": "受惠北都屯門吉田大廈招租 整層樓面近7萬呎",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"受惠北都屯門吉田大廈招租 整層樓面近7萬呎\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/4d186c43c631dcabda9b10f9052518f9/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250313/_2025031312054275994.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">受惠北都屯門吉田大廈招租 整層樓面近7萬呎</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>北部都會區發展下，屯門作為連通北都和機場的重要樞紐，獲工業、科技和物流公司進駐，區內大型工廈吉田大廈招租，同層單位可連通，形成面積近7萬方呎樓面，屬罕見的大型整層樓面。\n\n</p><h2>距西鐵站步程5分鐘</h2>\n<p>世邦魏理仕發言人表示，吉田大廈一期為一幢5層高工廈，總樓面約13萬方呎，而二期及三期分別為22層及23層高工廈，二、三期同層兩個三萬多方呎單位可連通，形成近7萬方呎樓面，屬罕有的大型樓面，該廈大部分樓層已安裝冷氣供租客使用。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4134426/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"屯門吉田工廈屬區內地標工廈。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d58be088278949499ef83e4d689b5628/2025-03/2025-03-13_120023.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        屯門吉田工廈屬區內地標工廈。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>她續說，該廈位於屯門中心位置，距離西鐵屯門路站僅5分鐘步程，可透過巴士、小巴和輕軌直接抵達。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2057876/即時-地產-受惠北都屯門吉田大廈招租-整層樓面近7萬呎",
            "pub_date": "2025-03-13 12:11:44",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "警港島反黑打擊黃賭毒 拘74男女檢$160萬毒品",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"警方檢獲大批證物。劉漢權攝\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/19e0f86781b95fdf41ad7cb8eb9d5858/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250313/_2025031312021356241.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">警方檢獲大批證物。劉漢權攝</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>警方過去10日在港島區展開打擊三合會行動，搗破多個賣淫場所和賭檔，並掃蕩販毒罪行，堵截黑社會收入來源。行動中人員共拘捕74名男女，檢獲包括太空油在內、總值超過160萬元的毒品。\n\n</p>\n<p>港島總區刑事部聯同港島各警區人員，於本月3日至12日採取代號為「智鼓」的行動，打擊三合會罪行及堵截其非法收入，共拘捕74名人士，搗破5個賣淫場所和6個賭檔，包括1個非法麻雀館、2個百家樂賭檔及3個釣魚機賭檔，檢獲大量賭具和逾25萬現金。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4134301/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/4f0e97040a47b623d33b84e1d4b9b795/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250313_111252695_04.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4134302/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f89bd0179f5fce3b8b930f1eddf75a20/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250313_111252695_05.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4134303/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1026173bfba8044add90de0bb638a7cf/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250313_111252695_06.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4134305/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/4bf642ae0f53836183e3fab1034d9adf/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250313_111252695_08.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4134300/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/06796028262602da298197d9a495ea5b/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250313_111252695_03.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4134307/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f6f40ac32e319e160237a152f488e6cd/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250313_111252695_09.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>行動中包括7個反毒品執法，其間以涉嫌「販運危險藥物」和「串謀販運危險藥物」罪拘捕9人，檢獲多種毒品，分別有40克可卡因、327克霹靂可卡因、34克冰毒、12克K仔、987支大麻油、2.3公斤大麻和36支太空油毒品等；毒品總市值超過160萬元。行動期間，探員亦偵破區內多宗與三合會有關案件，包括傷人案和刑事毀壞案。\n\n</p>\n<p>被捕的74人包括41男33女，他們介乎19至70歲，部分人有三合會背景，他們分別涉嫌「經營非法賭博場所」、「在非法賭博場所內賭博」、「販運危險藥物」、「管有危險藥物」、「自稱三合會」、「刑事毀壞」、「傷人」、「行使偽鈔」及「盜竊」等。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4134308/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/eb65a6c8c9bb5e07d76a8a1b7cf41da4/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250313_111252695_10.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4134310/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1c44a4b11464d6280d9c9e4814db6762/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250313_111252695_12.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4134311/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a08cd68236c7bfee04932663d89bdf4c/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250313_111252695_13.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4134328/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"港島總區反三合會行動組高級督察吳嘉倫。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b39de45012bca00275557bd9243c0c1a/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250313_111252695.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        港島總區反三合會行動組高級督察吳嘉倫。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4134330/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"吳嘉倫講述案件。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/5e28724205d3f06be7357d5680fc21c1/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250313_111252695_02.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        吳嘉倫講述案件。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4134329/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/76ef6d48b62f0611aab8a7237fe80ab1/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250313_111252695_01.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>港島總區反三合會行動組高級督察吳嘉倫稱，警方發現有業主將物業出租，但被用開設賣淫場所或賭檔。他提醒業主有責任在出租單位時，了解其用途，如有懷疑應報警求助。另外，警方亦發現有人在網上平台兜售太空油毒品，吳強調太空油毒品禍害嚴重，去年就有130人因吸食太空油不適需要送院，當中3人死亡，他呼籲家長要留意子女的社交圈子。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2057875/即時-港聞-警港島反黑打擊黃賭毒-拘74男女檢-160萬毒品",
            "pub_date": "2025-03-13 12:06:14",
            "source": "stheadline",
