            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "啟德地盤工遭剷車輾傷腳  鮮血狂湧",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"工人腳部遭剷車輾過。fb：交通意外關注組(香港)\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/f4a3d501976d12ce421a86fe0b9fb805/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250313/_2025031312002761471.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">工人腳部遭剷車輾過。fb：交通意外關注組(香港)</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>今（13日）晨10時52分，啟德沐禮街某地盤發生工傷意外，一名工人遭剷車輾過腳部，傷口鮮血狂湧，由救護車送院治理。網上圖片顯示，傷者坐在地上，長褲輾爛，鮮血染紅地上一灘水，相當駭人。\n\n</p>\n<p> \n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4134417/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"工人腳部遭剷車輾過。fb：交通意外關注組(香港)\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/980ad9739bb65879af8ce395871d5c8e/2025-03/01_1_6.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        工人腳部遭剷車輾過。fb：交通意外關注組(香港)\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
